    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "丫鬟",
        "小龙",
        "来在了花园门用目观看",
        "杨氏",
        "都只为庙残破欲修宫殿"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": "杨氏",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴家生来命运差，嫁个丈夫丑如麻。纵有家财无处用，终朝念佛把香插。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我杨氏。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（丫鬟暗上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嫁与金钱子为妻，虽有家财万贯。怎奈他长的四六不成材，三分不像人，七分"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倒像鬼。我不见他倒好。一见他我就有气。每天无事，只是烧香念佛。这日子"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也不知到何日是个了吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说大奶奶，我自嫁了您们大爷，吃的是珍馐美味，穿的是绫罗绸缎，哪有一"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "点不好？等到明年，再生养一位少爷，您岂不是更乐啦吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你再也不要说啦。不提养儿子到好，提起了养儿子，反倒叫我生气。你看你们"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大爷，那个长相儿，三分不像人，七分倒像鬼，不见他倒好，一见他我就生气。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大奶奶，您倒不要这样说。我们大爷，虽然相貌丑陋，到了晚上，办起事来，"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "同人家是一样的滋味。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我告诉你说罢，我宁可一辈子长斋，我也不贪他那一口荤食。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大奶奶也不必烦闷，咱们到花园里去玩玩去，好不好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此带路。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨氏",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "艳阳日春光好花红一片，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨氏",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "桃花红杨柳绿百鸟声喧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨氏",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "又只见双燕子飞落池边。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（小龙上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "小龙",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "离却了莲花塘大街游玩，"
        },
        {
          "character": "小龙",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "有男女和老少闹嚷声喧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "小龙",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "假装做一道士沿门化缘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "小龙",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "来在了花园门用目观看"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀，这门外头，是什么人在此敲木鱼儿，待我出去看看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳呀，敢自是一位小道士在这里化缘呐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说大奶奶，瞧您门外头，来了一位小道童，在咱们这儿化缘呐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我出去看看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说那一位道童，你是从哪里来的？你要一一讲来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "小龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "小龙",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "家住在盘陀山玄真庙院，"
        },
        {
          "character": "小龙",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "每日里在山中修道参禅。"
        },
        {
          "character": "小龙",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "因此上求施主资助银钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "小龙",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "都只为庙残破欲修宫殿"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来如此，你请进来坐坐罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "对啦，我们大奶奶是最爱行善的。你今天可是来巧啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说你还不曾吃饭啦罢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "小龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这……正是。不曾用饭。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那么你就随我来罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨氏拉小龙同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好吓，我们大奶奶，今天可遇见了小白脸好面孔的人啦。我去跟着他们，看他"
        }
      ],
