    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "丫鬟",
        "小龙",
        "杨氏",
        "金钱子"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨氏引小龙同上，丫鬟随上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "小龙",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "男贪女爱多缱绻，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨氏",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千里姻缘一线牵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "小龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "娘子请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请坐，我说你这样的年轻，你也有点道行靡有？"
        },
        {
          "character": "小龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若问俺的神通，俺降妖捉怪，无一不能。俺看你这里妖气冲天，定有妖魔鬼怪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么，这儿有妖怪，那倒巧啦。就请你就替我们给捉捉吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（金钱子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "金钱子",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将身来在卧房外，"
        },
        {
          "character": "金钱子",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "见一道童怒冲怀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "金钱子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胆大道童，来到我的卧房作甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "方才我说有妖怪，果然妖怪来了，"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这不是妖怪，这就是我们家的大爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "小龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你说不是妖怪，这一时三刻，管叫他化为脓血而亡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "小龙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天灵灵，地灵灵，唵嘛呢，叭咪吽。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（金钱子倒地。火彩。风婆、雨师、雷公、电母同上。小龙急下。风婆、雨师、雷公、电母同追下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳呀，可吓死我啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳呀，我的妈呀，这一刻的工夫，我们大爷也化成了血泥啦.这小道童，也被"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "雷给殛啦，这怎么好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨氏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "从今以后，我可再也不敢相遇人啦。阿弥陀佛。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨氏、丫鬟同下。）"
        }
      ],
