    {
      "scene_index": 7,
      "label": "第七场",
      "characters_present": [
        "孙悟空",
        "达摩"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙悟空上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我道是谁，原来是达摩祖师。"
        },
        {
          "character": "达摩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是大圣，吾这里稽首了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我闲听人言，你在那少林寺，参禅悟道，养性修真。面壁九年，头上喜鹊成巢，"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "耳朵内长出青草来，人人都道你圆寂了。怎么你还不会死么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "达摩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾本无生，哪得有死？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "阿弥陀佛。"
        },
        {
          "character": "达摩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大圣，我看你匆匆忙忙，莫非也要往昊天路上去么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳呀祖师吓！此事你还不知道么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "达摩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾却不晓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只因莲花塘，赤发虬龙作乱，水淹百里，伤害无数生灵。玉帝大怒，点动天兵"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天将，扫荡孽龙。连俺老孙，也在其内。"
        },
        {
          "character": "达摩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来如此。看今日你我相逢，可算有缘，吾同你去到十洲三岛游玩一回，你意"
        },
        {
          "character": "达摩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不得工夫，改日再会。少陪了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙悟空下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "达摩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看这个猴头，头也不回。竟自去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（端正好） 你看他，势匆匆，"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "孙悟空→达摩",
          "turns": 6
